          "slidetitle": "Mitigating AI Investment Risks",
          "subtitle": "Strategies to Reduce Exposure and Risk",
          "slidecontent": "• Always verify AI-generated insights against independent, human-curated sources before acting\n• Cross-check recommendations\n• Treat AI outputs as a starting point, not a final decision\n• Establish clear internal policies on how and when AI tools may be used in your investment process\n• Regularly audit AI tools for accuracy, bias, and consistency over time\n• Document every AI-assisted decision to maintain accountability and support future review"
