          "slidetitle": "Key Points to Remember",
          "subtitle": "What every analyst must bear in mind",
          "slidecontent": "• AI tools can generate confident-sounding analysis even when the underlying data is outdated or simply wrong\n• Always verify AI outputs against primary sources\n• Hallucinated figures and fabricated citations are a real risk, not a theoretical one\n• Regulatory accountability still rests with you, not the tool\n• Treat AI as a first draft, not a final answer\n• As a next step, build a simple checklist for reviewing any AI-generated insight before it reaches a client or decision-maker"
